He was 15 years old and a pupil at Townview High School in Krugersdorp when this picture was taken in 2003. The future of South Africa lies with the youth of today and this year, Youth Month will be commemorated under the theme “Live the Legacy: Towards A socio-economically empowered youth”. The Saturday Star would like to celebrate its readers and their contribution to a better South Africa. So we are asking you to send us your school picture and we will publish it in the paper this Saturday. Send us your name and surname, your age at the time, the name of the school and in  which year the picture was taken to kashiefa.ajam@inl.co.za or karishma.dipa@inl.co.za